comments.body: This version had some problems which I had to fix and bump version for internal reasons, which led to me calling register again as per Registrator.jl's README. However, instead of the changes being pushed into this PR, they were pushed into a new one: https://github.com/JuliaRegistries/General/pull/3222. I assume this PR can be ignored/closed in favor of the new one.
